    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Neko's Rage is a very dynamic 2D action game in which you play as a cyborg. Fight hordes of robots and collect more resources to improve your character, your equipments and to restore your hub.<br>Rush to explode the bio-robotic creatures which are spreading more and more quickly in the differents biomes, the more time passes and the more hostile the environment becomes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/c6c7f61ef4a560d86101d7ed302db17c.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/c6c7f61ef4a560d86101d7ed302db17c.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/c6c7f61ef4a560d86101d7ed302db17c.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>A post apocalyptic future</u></strong></h2>In 2130 human beings become obsolete and unadapted to the world's pandemic and climatic conditions, bio-mechanical creatures have become the dominant species, but to awaken they need one of the last biological sources of energy on earth , the humans ...<br>Neko Units are invented to fight and free captive humans of the machines's incubation nests.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/d530f35f1a0b5e981eec15a0d12f0513.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/d530f35f1a0b5e981eec15a0d12f0513.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/d530f35f1a0b5e981eec15a0d12f0513.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Gameplay and a lot of action</u></strong></h2>You will gain powers with a lots of upgrades and equipments to buy in Gentech's laboratory but also in battle's stages with a lots of differents capacities amplificators or by killing enemies without taking damage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/d7ef90e5fb8db659862eced66955446b.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/d7ef90e5fb8db659862eced66955446b.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/d7ef90e5fb8db659862eced66955446b.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>The Neko-chain</u></strong></h2>A chain counter that totals the number of enemies killed in a row, this influences the player's luck rate and allows you to obtain more items and better qualities in chests or by killing enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/f787ffb5b3f1d282db908919ef5e12c7.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/f787ffb5b3f1d282db908919ef5e12c7.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/f787ffb5b3f1d282db908919ef5e12c7.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>The overheat and enraged mode</u></strong></h2>When the destruction of enemies is linked without being hit your character will go into enraged mode, increased critical hit rate, more speed and the possibility of cross dash attacks to generate even more damage and experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/5338e1a4d02b6a2da4ccb7f51df14f50.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/5338e1a4d02b6a2da4ccb7f51df14f50.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/5338e1a4d02b6a2da4ccb7f51df14f50.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Stage procedural building</u></strong></h2>The stages are proceduraly generated to make every run different and fun.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/0a7c3531c06af005128b0d9ec6f35104.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/0a7c3531c06af005128b0d9ec6f35104.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/0a7c3531c06af005128b0d9ec6f35104.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Find cracked walls for more resources<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/dc3b8ebe8d93116125014fdbbcac770d.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/dc3b8ebe8d93116125014fdbbcac770d.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/dc3b8ebe8d93116125014fdbbcac770d.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Find invisible chest<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/0796445fb76de47dabb936073636db7f.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/0796445fb76de47dabb936073636db7f.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/0796445fb76de47dabb936073636db7f.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight dangerous foes<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/27e3b3da73afd1e2b81021efd8753eea.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/27e3b3da73afd1e2b81021efd8753eea.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/27e3b3da73afd1e2b81021efd8753eea.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Buy upgrades and equipment at Gentech<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/ded9bdc561f2a99f477bd1e6ab16f27d.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/ded9bdc561f2a99f477bd1e6ab16f27d.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/ded9bdc561f2a99f477bd1e6ab16f27d.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Test your skill to collect more resources<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/f52297fc990b9c1526d8c6924875e5fc.poster.avif?t=1757430860\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/f52297fc990b9c1526d8c6924875e5fc.webm?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362330/extras/f52297fc990b9c1526d8c6924875e5fc.mp4?t=1757430860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
